name: WORLD UNITE! - NO WAR
description:
Charity work to support Ukraine in it fight against Putin's invasion. The world must unite to stop this war and to let democracy prevail. This war is a humanitarian crisis started by a small minded autocrat to quench his thirst for power. It must end. 

If we can all pull a string against fascism, the whole ball will unravel.

All proceeds will be donated to charity organizations in support of Ukraine relief via the KT1DWnLiUkNtAQDErXxudFEH63JC6mqg3HEx wallet set up by fxhash and versum.
